      <span class="headers">PoP: Aid Grimel Quest - Shopping List</span>
<p>
<p>I will break the quest down by items needed for each segment of the quest, and then by vendor purchased, mob dropped, and foraged items/ground spawn. At the end of each section, I include any very basic utility items that weren't mentioned above, such basic items that we should all know the recipes to them anyway and don't need a shopping list for them.</p>

<p>Items which cannot be made by everyone and therefore can only be made by a friend or bought in the bazaar will be broken out as well. This is where things get a little sloppy--I include the things you need to purchase to have a friend do the combine in the general list and mark it with an *, and the things those items make in a separate section. If an item is used twice in a combine, once for an unrestricted subcombine, and once for a restricted subcombine, it is listed twice in the appropriate quantities for each subcombine.</p>

<p>This does NOT include the items given to you for each quest received from Aid Grimel. NODROP items will be identified as such, otherwise everything is droppable.</p>

<p>If I miss anything, or if you can think of a better way to organize this, let me know.</p>

<h4><a href="http://www.eqtraders.com//articles/article_page.php?article=q172&menustr=120055000000">PART 1 - BLACKSMITHING</a></h4>

<ul>
<li>Vendor Purchased</li>
<ul>
<li>1 - Jar of Acid</li>
<li>1 - Spell: Imbue Diamond</li>
</ul>
<li>Mob Dropped</li>
<ul>
<li>3 - Sandstorm Pearl</li>
<li>1 - A Drop of Pure Rain</li>
<li>1 - Storm Rider Blood</li>
<li>2 - Nightmare Mephit Blood *</li>
<li>1 - Nightmare Mephit Blood</li>
<li>2 - Raw Diamond *</li>
<li>1 - Raw Diamond</li>
</ul>
<li>Restricted Combines (purchaseable in The Bazaar, or made by a friend using the * marked items above)</li>
<ul>
<li>2 - Black Diamond of Nightmares (spell cast by Enchanters or Necromancers, level 62+)</li>
</ul>
<li>Utility Items not included above:</li>
<ul>
<li>3 - Celestial Essence</li>
</ul>
</ul>

<h4><a href="http://www.eqtraders.com//articles/article_page.php?article=q173&menustr=120055000000">PART 2 - BREWING</a></h4>

<ul>
<li>Vendor Purchased</li>
<ul>
<li>18 - Water Flask</li>
<li>6 - Soda</li>
<li>6 - Yarrow</li>
<li>6 - Bottle</li>
<li>6 - Cork</li>
<li>1 - Cogs *</li>
<li>1 - Gears *</li>
<li>1 - Grease *</li>
<li>1 - Sprockets *</li>
</ul>
<li>Mob Dropped</li>
<ul>
<li>1 - Blue Diamond *</li>
</ul>
<li>Foraged/Ground Spawn</li>
<ul>
<li>1 - Branch of Sylvan Oak *</li>
<li>6 - A Strange Dark Fungus</li>
<li>6 - Underfoot Mushroom</li>
</ul>
<li>Restricted Combines (purchaseable in The Bazaar, or made by a friend using the * marked items above)</li>
<ul>
<li>1 - Corking Device (made by a Gnome with Tinkering skill)</li>
</ul>
<li>Utility Items not included above:</li>
<ul>
<li>9 - Celestial Essence</li>
</ul>
</ul>

<h4><a href="http://www.eqtraders.com//articles/article_page.php?article=q174&menustr=120055000000">PART 3 - JEWELCRAFT</a></h4>

<ul>
<li>Vendor Purchased</li>
<ul>
<li>2 - Water Flask</li>
<li>2 - Velium Bar</li>
<li>3 - Velium Bar *</li>
<li>1 - Spell: Enchant Velium *</li>
<li>1 - Coldain Velium Temper</li>
</ul>
<li>Mod Dropped</li>
<ul>
<li>1 - Blue Diamond</li>
</ul>
<li>Other - Acquired via NPCs</li>
<ul>
<li>1 - Coldain Smithing Hammer</li>
<li>1 - Etching Tools</li>
</ul>
<li>Restricted Combines (purchaseable in The Bazaar, or made by a friend using the * marked items above)</li>
<ul>
<li>3 - Enchanted Velium Bar (spell cast by an Enchanter)</li>
</ul>
<li>Utility Items not included above:</li>
<ul>
<li>1 - Celestial Essence</li>
</ul>
</ul>

<h4><a href="http://www.eqtraders.com//articles/article_page.php?article=q175&menustr=120055000000">PART 4 - POTTERY</a></h4>

<ul>
<li>Vendor Purchased</li>
<ul>
<li>3 - Jar of Lacquer</li>
<li>3 - Opal</li>
<li>3 - Water Flask</li>
<li>1 - Poison Vial *</li>
<li>4 - Ruby *</li>
<li>1 - Spell: Purify Mana *</li>
<li>1 - Spell:Enchant Clay *</li>
<li>3 - Large Block of Clay *</li>
<li>3 - Limestone</li>
<li>3 - Lead Sulphide</li>
<li>1 - Sculpting Tools</li>
</ul>
<li>Mob Dropped</li>
<ul>
<li>3 - Iron Oxide (may also be ground spawn)</li>
<li>3 - Permafrost Crystals (may also be ground spawn)</li>
<li>3 - Sacred Water NODROP ITEM</li>
</ul>
<li>Restricted Combines (purchaseable in The Bazaar, or made by a friend using the * marked items above)</li>
<ul>
<li>3 - Large Block of Magic Clay (spell cast by Enchanters)</li>
<li>1 - Vial of Purified Mana (spell cast by Enchanter)</li>
</ul>
<li>Utility Items not included above:</li>
<ul>
<li>1 - Ceramic Lining</li>
</ul>
</ul>

<h4><a href="http://www.eqtraders.com//articles/article_page.php?article=q176&menustr=120055000000">PART 5 - TAILORING</a></h4>

<ul>
<li>Vendor Purchased</li>
<ul>
<li>3 - Poison Vial *</li>
<li>12 - Ruby *</li>
<li>1 - Spell: Purify Mana *</li>
<li>1 - Spell: Imbue Diamond</li>
<li>1 - Tunic Pattern</li>
<li>1 - Blank Emblem</li>
</ul>
<li>Mob Dropped</li>
<ul>
<li>6 - Fire Arachnid Silk</li>
<li>1 - Fire Mephit Blood *</li>
<li>1 - Fire Mephit Blood</li>
<li>1 - Raw Diamond *</li>
<li>1 - Raw Diamond</li>
<li>1 - Brick of Molten Ore</li>
<li>3 - Obsidianwood Sap</li>
</ul>
<li>Restricted Combines (purchaseable in The Bazaar, or made by a friend using the * marked items above)</li>
<ul>
<li>3 - Vial of Purified Mana (spell cast by Enchanter)</li>
<li>1 - Red Diamond of Fire (Spell Cast by Enchanter or Magician, level 65+)</li>
</ul>
</ul>

<h4><a href="http://www.eqtraders.com//articles/article_page.php?article=q177&menustr=120055000000">PART 6 - FLETCHING</a></h4>

<ul>
<li>Vendor Purchased</li>
<ul>
<li>1 - Clump of Wax</li>
<li>2 - Cam Parts Mold</li>
<li>1 - Planing Tool</li>
</ul>
<li>Mob Dropped</li>
<ul>
<li>2 - Air Arachnid Silk</li>
<li>2 - Chunk of Wind Metal</li>
<li>1 - Featherwood Bow Staff</li>
</ul>
<li>Foraged Items</li>
<ul>
<li>4 - Clockwork Grease *</li>
</ul>
<li>Restricted Combines (purchaseable in The Bazaar, or made by a friend using the * marked items above)</li>
<ul>
<li>2 - Wind Metal Bow Cam</li>
</ul>
<li>Utility Items not included above:</li>
<ul>
<li>1 - File</li>
<li>2 - Small Clay Jar</li>
</ul>
</ul>

<h4><a href="http://www.eqtraders.com//articles/article_page.php?article=q178&menustr=120055000000">PART 7 - BAKING</a></h4>

<ul>
<li>Vendor Purchased</li>
<ul>
<li>4 - Frosting</li>
<li>4 - Bottle of Milk</li>
<li>2 - Rennet</li>
<li>1 - Cup of Flour</li>
<li>3 - Spices</li>
<li>1 - Jug of Sauces</li>
<li>2 - Vinegar</li>
<li>2 - Loaf of Bread</li>
<li>2 - Metal Rod *</li>
<li>1 - Water Flask</li>
</ul>
<li>Mob Dropped</li>
<ul>
<li>1 - Any combination of the following: Slarghilug Leg, Unbroken Eye Stalk, Webbed Tail Fin</li>
<li>4 - Hero Parts</li>
<li>1 - Regrua Claws</li>
<li>1 - Knuckle Joint *</li>
</ul>
<li>Foraged Items</li>
<ul>
<li>4 - Planar Fruit</li>
<li>1 - Habenero Pepper</li>
<li>3 - Vegetables</li>
</ul>
<li>Restricted Combines (purchaseable in The Bazaar, or made by a friend using the * marked items above)</li>
<ul>
<li>1 - Crab Cracker</li>
</ul>
<li>Utility Items not included above:</li>
<ul>
<li>8 - Celestial Essence</li>
<li>4 - Clump of Dough</li>
<li>1 - Muffin Tin</li>
<li>1 - Dairy Spoon</li>
<li>1 - Non-stick Frying Pan</li>
<li>1 - Smoker</li>
<li>1 - Firewater *</li>
<li>1 - Bucket</li>
<li>2 - Picnic Basket</li>
</ul>
</ul>
<h4>SOME HANDY TALLIES OF ITEMS USED IN MULTIPLE PARTS OF THE QUEST:</h4>
 (total amount used over entire quest)
<ul>
<li>21 - Celestial Essence</li>
<li>5 - Raw Diamond</li>
<li>4 - Vial of Purified Mana (spell cast by Enchanter)</li>
<li>45 - Water Flask (including those used in the making of the Utility Items and their subcombines)</li>
</ul>

<p>This shopping list created by Huntress Ambrya Naturechild</p>

